xt\": \"Albert\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Show\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"high performance director Michael Blake\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 208}, {\"ngram\": \"high performance\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 238}, {\"ngram\": \"their selections\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 280}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 307}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitions\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 330}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 343}, {\"ngram\": \"late July\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Blake selected Daniel Coyle with the horse Legacy, Cian O'Connor with the horse Maurice and Shane Sweetnam with the hose James Kann Cruz for nomination to the Olympic Federation of Ireland.\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 410, \"end\": 423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cian_O'Connor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cian O'Connor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cian_O'Connor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cian_O'Connor\"}, {\"begin\": 480, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.6374162235671224, \"rank\": 0.5461819791074948, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Blake\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"Daniel Coyle\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 386}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse Legacy\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 408}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"Maurice\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"Shane Sweetnam\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 465}, {\"ngram\": \"the hose\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"nomination\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Federation\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"Ireland\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The P Alternate combination will be Bertram Allen with the horse Pacino Amiro.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertram_Allen_(equestrian)\", \"score\": 0.9999994781698203, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bertram Allen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertram_Allen_(equestrian)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertram_Allen_(equestrian)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The P Alternate combination\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 577}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"Pacino Amiro\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Blake said: \\\"It is the greatest honour for an athlete to be chosen to represent their country at an Olympic Games and I am delighted to have chosen these athletes for consideration for Paris.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 815, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999875210435094, \"rank\": 1.2479112167197716e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Blake\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest honour\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"their country\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 743}, {\"ngram\": \"these athletes\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"consideration\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are enjoying an excellent period of Irish jumping at the moment and it is testament to the riders and all of their teams who look after the horses at home, and when they compete, that they have all reached such a high level.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an excellent period\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"testament\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"the riders\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"their teams\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"the horses\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"such a high level\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The athletes and horses I have chosen have been performing brilliantly, week-in-week-out, on the international stage and we will give it everything we have to achieve what we are setting out to do.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"week-out\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"the international stage\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would like to thank the Olympic Federation of Ireland, Sport Ireland, Horse Sport Ireland and everyone involved in show jumping in Ireland for their support and I hope we will do everyone proud.\\\"\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1311, \"end\": 1324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sport Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1326, \"end\": 1345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_Sport_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Horse Sport Ireland\",